<br>
[25% + (Dual Wield or Celtic Dual Skill x .5)%]<br>
<br>
<br>
However, recently, through player logs and experimentation, we believe the formula may be:<br>
<br>
[25% + (Dual Wield or Celtic Dual Skill x .5)% + (Character Level x .25%)]<br>
