<br>
Check to see if double swing.<br>
If double swing, swing both blades and delay will average of 2 weapons.<br>
If not a double swing and you are not using a style, you have a 50/50 chance for either weapon to swing. Delay will be that of the swinging weapon.<br>
If not a double swing and you are using a style, swing the main hand weapon. Delay will be that of the main hand weapon.<br>
