<br>
LA (50th Zerk angaints lvl 0 mobs)<br>
50+8 LA<br>
Main hand with one weapon<br>
205<br>
Main hand with 2 weapons<br>
170<br>
=82.92% dmg total of 165.84% dmg<br>
50+2 LA<br>
Main hand one weapon<br>
205<br>
Main hand 2 weapons<br>
166<br>
=80.97% dmg total of 161.94% dmg<br>
